1
00:00:47,781 --> 00:00:49,078
Take.

2
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:51,546
Sir...?

3
00:00:51,751 --> 00:00:53,218
He's in the car.

4
00:00:54,421 --> 00:00:56,889
Nandu, 3 special teas.

5
00:00:56,956 --> 00:00:57,888
Haven't they come yet?

6
00:00:58,091 --> 00:00:59,058
lt seems they have left for here.

7
00:01:02,062 --> 00:01:03,495
Who will serve water?
Your father?

8
00:01:03,897 --> 00:01:04,727
Sir, he's new to the job.

9
00:01:04,964 --> 00:01:06,124
Have you ordered tea for Sir?

10
00:01:06,232 --> 00:01:08,792
l have sir. Come on boy!

11
00:01:20,246 --> 00:01:21,713
Stay here till he
finishes his tea.

12
00:01:55,148 --> 00:01:56,115
Hey Bloody bastard!

13
00:01:56,316 --> 00:01:58,147
Bloody kid!
How dare to kill my boss!

14
00:01:58,351 --> 00:02:00,581
Hey stop! l'll kill you.

15
00:02:04,157 --> 00:02:08,457
Afternoon...20 minutes after the matinee
show of 'Agniparvatham'. Rainy season.

16
00:02:15,668 --> 00:02:19,331
Sir, l'll do any work.
Just feed me.

17
00:02:19,606 --> 00:02:20,504
No need to pay me.
- Get lost boy!

18
00:02:20,707 --> 00:02:21,173
What?

19
00:02:21,374 --> 00:02:22,966
He's pestering since morning.

20
00:02:23,176 --> 00:02:25,406
He's asking for work.
- lsn't he saying no work?

21
00:02:25,612 --> 00:02:27,876
You clear out boy...
- l was earlier working in a shop...

22
00:02:28,081 --> 00:02:30,413
...selling tea...
please recommend to him.

23
00:02:30,617 --> 00:02:32,016
Please ask him to hire me.

24
00:02:35,922 --> 00:02:37,856
Where did you work earlier?
- Suryapet.

25
00:02:46,065 --> 00:02:46,690
Nandu.

26
00:02:48,334 --> 00:02:49,494
Yesterday he bumped off Suri.

27
00:02:49,869 --> 00:02:50,494
Suri?

28
00:02:50,737 --> 00:02:51,465
Vanka Suri.

29
00:02:51,704 --> 00:02:52,398
Vanka Suri?

30
00:02:52,605 --> 00:02:54,129
He's a big mafia don
in Vijayawada West.

31
00:02:54,340 --> 00:02:56,103
People stop drinking water
on hearing his name.

32
00:02:56,609 --> 00:02:57,871
May be water problem?

33
00:03:01,881 --> 00:03:02,848
First time?

34
00:03:05,785 --> 00:03:06,615
Good start!

35
00:03:07,053 --> 00:03:07,849
Shall l take him into our fold?

36
00:03:09,389 --> 00:03:10,356
First feed him.

37
00:03:10,557 --> 00:03:16,723
Lakshmivilas Bank...the bank Sadhu
is planning to rob...night 1 :42 am...

38
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:29,904
Malli...you stay here.
Nandu, you come with me.

39
00:03:30,109 --> 00:03:30,905
Move...move...

40
00:03:40,286 --> 00:03:41,014
Move..move..

41
00:03:45,525 --> 00:03:46,651
Chanti, you watch the back.

42
00:03:47,427 --> 00:03:48,655
Where's the gelatin, Manik?

43
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,807
Join the two wires.

44
00:04:02,709 --> 00:04:03,539
Come out fast.

45
00:04:06,546 --> 00:04:07,205
Open it now.

46
00:04:23,029 --> 00:04:24,963
Nandu, faster...faster...

47
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,863
Come on move...move...

48
00:04:30,236 --> 00:04:30,930
Start the vehicle.

49
00:04:58,364 --> 00:05:00,559
Had a nice journey, Sadhu?

50
00:05:09,175 --> 00:05:11,666
Your man Narsing,
changed sides, that's all!.

51
00:05:17,784 --> 00:05:20,719
Looks like someone's hard
earned money, it's smelling sweat.

52
00:05:21,487 --> 00:05:23,216
That's for you and
this is for me, now clear out.

53
00:05:29,429 --> 00:05:31,897
No problem...can withstand
another round also.

54
00:05:32,432 --> 00:05:34,195
Hey, Order teas!

55
00:05:55,822 --> 00:05:58,848
Where are the candles?

56
00:06:22,682 --> 00:06:27,142
That S.l. will definitely kill me.

57
00:06:28,721 --> 00:06:30,484
lf you stay with me,
he'll kill you also.

58
00:06:31,224 --> 00:06:33,658
Go...go away.

59
00:06:35,194 --> 00:06:37,924
He'll not come boss.
l've killed him.

60
00:06:41,234 --> 00:06:51,200
i Dream.

61
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:23,969
He's a one man army.

62
00:07:24,444 --> 00:07:28,676
He's the new sun to
rise in the dark world.

63
00:07:43,663 --> 00:07:47,724
He's an unchallenged hero.

64
00:07:48,167 --> 00:07:52,570
He's the fiery hero to give
jitters to the tsunami.

65
00:08:57,303 --> 00:09:01,865
lf time chases me,
l'll attack it.

66
00:09:02,074 --> 00:09:06,773
it chooses war,
l'll win over it.

67
00:09:16,222 --> 00:09:18,213
l'm a thunder...

68
00:09:18,424 --> 00:09:20,654
l'm a lightning...

69
00:09:20,893 --> 00:09:23,054
l'm the fire...

70
00:09:23,262 --> 00:09:27,062
l'm cool rain...

71
00:10:08,574 --> 00:10:13,068
He's the ray of light
in pitch darkness.

72
00:10:13,212 --> 00:10:18,377
He's the shore to withstand
the fury of waves.

73
00:10:27,593 --> 00:10:32,326
Mustering courage from self,
overcoming all the hurdles...

74
00:10:32,531 --> 00:10:34,658
...fighting it out everyday of life...

75
00:10:34,867 --> 00:10:38,564
...he's the man of hour.

76
00:10:50,249 --> 00:10:55,744
A road in the Old City...
Second Namaz is in progress...

77
00:11:12,672 --> 00:11:13,297
Has he come?

78
00:11:14,006 --> 00:11:16,907
Watching...matinee show...

79
00:11:18,344 --> 00:11:19,333
Where will you be?

80
00:11:20,613 --> 00:11:22,604
Next street...Red colour Ford.

81
00:11:23,983 --> 00:11:24,711
Be ready.

82
00:11:25,584 --> 00:11:26,346
l'll come immediately
after finishing the job.

83
00:11:26,552 --> 00:11:27,416
Don't delay.

84
00:11:43,436 --> 00:11:44,368
Buy whatever you want.

85
00:11:52,912 --> 00:11:54,345
Kill the bastard, got it?

86
00:11:55,181 --> 00:11:55,943
Don't play with me.

87
00:11:56,148 --> 00:11:56,842
How about these?

88
00:11:57,316 --> 00:11:58,374
Okay...

89
00:12:00,086 --> 00:12:01,485
Okay...be careful.

90
00:12:03,856 --> 00:12:05,187
l want it to be done in 2 days.

91
00:12:05,725 --> 00:12:07,693
lf it is not done...beware...

92
00:12:08,427 --> 00:12:09,052
What else??

93
00:12:19,839 --> 00:12:22,899
Check all over the place.
Bloody killer shouldn't escape!

94
00:12:56,008 --> 00:12:58,135
Look, he's going there.

95
00:13:42,254 --> 00:13:43,516
Bloody! Move man!

96
00:13:43,722 --> 00:13:45,656
No way l'll not move.

97
00:14:39,278 --> 00:14:40,575
Won't they get tired!

98
00:14:41,113 --> 00:14:41,670
They can't jump.

99
00:15:23,722 --> 00:15:24,654
Greetings sir.

100
00:15:25,024 --> 00:15:26,218
Did l made you wait for long?

101
00:15:26,425 --> 00:15:28,120
l've been waiting for
10 years to become CM,

102
00:15:28,327 --> 00:15:29,954
10 minutes isn't a
big thing, sit down.

103
00:15:32,197 --> 00:15:33,061
CM is here.

104
00:15:38,938 --> 00:15:40,735
Opinion polls say
he'll make it again.

105
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,002
He shouldn't.

106
00:15:44,576 --> 00:15:48,672
Powerless politician
is like a widow.- Yes sir.

107
00:15:49,181 --> 00:15:50,512
Every man whistles at you.

108
00:15:53,953 --> 00:15:54,715
No value.

109
00:15:55,955 --> 00:15:58,753
Even people like you make them wait.
- No sir...

110
00:15:58,958 --> 00:15:59,856
Just for an example.

111
00:16:00,459 --> 00:16:03,656
This time we must do it,
otherwise no use.

112
00:16:04,430 --> 00:16:06,125
Already press has
forgotten me,

113
00:16:06,632 --> 00:16:07,621
it'll be very difficult
if people too forget me.

114
00:16:07,833 --> 00:16:08,925
Don't get dejected sir.

115
00:16:09,468 --> 00:16:10,435
Let's buy the votes
at Rs. 1000 a vote,

116
00:16:10,636 --> 00:16:12,501
still if we can't make it,
let's supply liquor freely.

117
00:16:12,705 --> 00:16:15,071
They will doze off having your drinks
and not come to vote for you.

118
00:16:15,274 --> 00:16:17,572
That will be better, we can cast
bogus votes ourselves.

119
00:16:17,776 --> 00:16:19,869
lf we as opposition can
rig the polls,

120
00:16:20,145 --> 00:16:23,512
think about what he can do
with the govt. under his control?

121
00:16:24,984 --> 00:16:26,042
Shall we bump him off?

122
00:16:26,251 --> 00:16:29,743
His wife will become CM
in the sympathy wave.

123
00:16:31,256 --> 00:16:32,223
What should we do then?

124
00:16:36,261 --> 00:16:37,489
Kill me!

125
00:16:42,034 --> 00:16:44,298
lf a boy comes home after
failing the tenth class,

126
00:16:44,603 --> 00:16:45,865
everyone at home will scold him.

127
00:16:46,472 --> 00:16:49,964
After seeing the result
if he attempts suicide,

128
00:16:50,242 --> 00:16:52,642
if public bring home
saving his life,

129
00:16:52,845 --> 00:16:54,312
everyone at home
will console him.

130
00:16:55,514 --> 00:16:58,415
ln the first case, people will be
angry on him for failing.

131
00:16:59,018 --> 00:16:59,985
ln the second case,

132
00:17:00,386 --> 00:17:02,411
there will be sympathy for
surviving the suicide attempt.

133
00:17:02,755 --> 00:17:03,915
l want that.

134
00:17:04,289 --> 00:17:05,119
Sympathy!

135
00:17:05,958 --> 00:17:07,983
So, there should be
an attempt on my life.

136
00:17:08,427 --> 00:17:09,519
But l must survive it.

137
00:17:10,696 --> 00:17:15,030
Farooq, our party election
campaign starts on the 10th.

138
00:17:15,467 --> 00:17:17,435
Stage manage an attempt
on my life the same day.

139
00:17:17,636 --> 00:17:19,263
l'll be admitted into a hospital,

140
00:17:19,705 --> 00:17:21,172
TV Channels will cover the news,

141
00:17:23,308 --> 00:17:26,971
few of my supporters will
immolate themselves.

142
00:17:27,946 --> 00:17:30,244
l'll campaign from
my hospital bed.

143
00:17:30,983 --> 00:17:32,780
l'll give an interview
sleeping on the stretcher.

144
00:17:33,352 --> 00:17:34,842
l'll cast my vote going
in a wheelchair.

145
00:17:35,054 --> 00:17:37,921
Excellent! Wheelchair to CM's chair!

146
00:17:38,824 --> 00:17:40,291
lt will cost you heavily sir.

147
00:17:40,492 --> 00:17:41,186
Why?

148
00:17:42,327 --> 00:17:44,727
There are people to kill
for Rs. 1 1 16 also,

149
00:17:45,230 --> 00:17:47,221
they will come from Bihar
to kill and then vanish.

150
00:17:47,900 --> 00:17:49,492
But if you want to survive the attack,

151
00:17:50,936 --> 00:17:52,096
we need professionals.

152
00:17:52,304 --> 00:17:53,669
Don't worry about money,

153
00:17:54,273 --> 00:17:55,399
get the best professional
in the market.

154
00:17:55,607 --> 00:17:58,201
No need to search for him,
he's here only.

155
00:17:58,877 --> 00:18:01,505
Yes sir, Hyderabad has
developed very much.

156
00:18:01,713 --> 00:18:03,180
We get anything we need here.

157
00:18:04,383 --> 00:18:05,407
Who is he?

158
00:18:25,037 --> 00:18:27,096
Not that...- He's here.

159
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:29,502
What?
- For you sir!

160
00:18:32,277 --> 00:18:34,108
Hello...who is that?

161
00:18:34,313 --> 00:18:35,837
Farooq asked me to contact you.

162
00:18:36,748 --> 00:18:39,046
One minute...talk to him.

163
00:18:40,152 --> 00:18:43,315
Hello...l'm Baji Reddy...go ahead.

164
00:18:43,522 --> 00:18:44,546
Give the phone to Siva Reddy.

165
00:18:44,756 --> 00:18:46,383
We both are one and same.

166
00:18:46,725 --> 00:18:48,283
ls it okay if l kill you
instead of him?

167
00:18:50,562 --> 00:18:51,688
Good joke.

168
00:18:51,897 --> 00:18:53,023
l can shoot well too.

169
00:18:54,900 --> 00:18:56,367
Yes, that is what we want.

170
00:18:57,469 --> 00:18:59,198
Farooq must have told
you everything.

171
00:18:59,471 --> 00:19:02,531
You must make the kill
but the victim must not die.

172
00:19:03,075 --> 00:19:03,700
1 .5

173
00:19:03,909 --> 00:19:05,877
How much?- 1 .5 crores.

174
00:19:06,078 --> 00:19:09,878
Too much. Any concession?

175
00:19:10,082 --> 00:19:11,879
Shall l kill you as a concession?

176
00:19:13,085 --> 00:19:14,882
Oh no! Thank you.

177
00:19:15,254 --> 00:19:17,722
75 lakhs in advance & 75 lakhs
after finishing the job.

178
00:19:17,923 --> 00:19:19,220
lf l get caught after
finishing the job...?

179
00:19:19,424 --> 00:19:21,051
What if you cheat me...?

180
00:19:21,293 --> 00:19:23,887
l know only to kill
not to cheat.

181
00:19:24,096 --> 00:19:27,395
Okay. l'll give it in one shot.

182
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:32,400
But it is a formality for us
to meet before the payment.

183
00:19:32,604 --> 00:19:33,571
Not necessary.

184
00:19:33,772 --> 00:19:36,070
lt is necessary for us.
We're giving you 1 .5 crores.

185
00:19:36,608 --> 00:19:38,735
Can't we atleast see your face?

186
00:19:38,944 --> 00:19:41,071
lf you want to see the gun,
nothing wrong.

187
00:19:41,647 --> 00:19:44,741
Want to see the bullet?
You'll be dead.

188
00:19:46,118 --> 00:19:48,416
The payment should be
in the denomination of 1000.

189
00:19:48,954 --> 00:19:52,583
Seal it in a plastic cover and
put it in a red color bag.

190
00:19:52,958 --> 00:19:56,917
Ask your man to take the
Begumpet local train by 9 pm.

191
00:19:57,129 --> 00:20:00,098
Tell him to keep the bag
below the seat & leave.

192
00:20:00,532 --> 00:20:02,261
Did he get down?- No sir.

193
00:20:02,968 --> 00:20:03,935
Keep watching.

194
00:20:04,536 --> 00:20:06,265
He'll get down with
our red color bag.

195
00:20:06,471 --> 00:20:09,269
Follow him, know his whereabouts
and inform me.- Okay sir.

196
00:20:11,476 --> 00:20:12,602
Sorry.- lts okay.

197
00:20:13,312 --> 00:20:15,280
What okay?- Nothing sir.

198
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:16,447
l said okay to him.

199
00:20:16,815 --> 00:20:18,783
Saw him?- He is not the one.

200
00:20:19,151 --> 00:20:21,779
lf it is not him,
it must be someone else.

201
00:20:22,654 --> 00:20:26,784
You idiot! lt is 1 .5 crores.

202
00:20:26,992 --> 00:20:27,959
lt took me a day to count.

203
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:29,627
Sir, the train is moving.

204
00:20:29,828 --> 00:20:32,126
Keep watching & it will go away.

205
00:20:32,331 --> 00:20:32,956
Yes sir.- Get into the train.

206
00:20:34,833 --> 00:20:39,793
ls the bag still there?
- Yes sir. But no money.

207
00:20:40,839 --> 00:20:44,639
He must have sat behind me
so that l won't be able to see him.

208
00:20:44,843 --> 00:20:45,810
He has taken the money.

209
00:21:00,058 --> 00:21:01,150
Were you reading a newspaper?

210
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:02,327
How did you know that?

211
00:21:02,527 --> 00:21:03,323
Nothing new about it.

212
00:21:03,528 --> 00:21:04,825
You were reading the paper and
he walked away with the money.

213
00:21:05,063 --> 00:21:05,995
What do you want me to do now?

214
00:21:06,198 --> 00:21:08,166
Catch a train & finish reading
the remaining newspaper.

215
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:10,334
Sir...- What?

216
00:21:11,737 --> 00:21:12,999
The bag is torn.

217
00:21:14,706 --> 00:21:16,333
No tension boy.

218
00:21:16,541 --> 00:21:18,168
Bring it here.
We'll get it stitched.

219
00:21:18,377 --> 00:21:24,009
Place of Siva Reddy's assassination...
night...time... (watch isn't working)

220
00:21:32,557 --> 00:21:34,525
l'll be in that building.
9th floor.

221
00:21:35,060 --> 00:21:37,187
Rent a car from some
unknown person.

222
00:21:38,230 --> 00:21:40,027
Look out for a new travel company.
- l need the license.

223
00:21:40,399 --> 00:21:41,525
Advance Rs. 10000.

224
00:21:51,243 --> 00:21:53,211
The meeting starts at 10:30 am
day after tomorrow.

225
00:21:53,412 --> 00:21:55,380
Wait on the road next
to the building.

226
00:22:19,604 --> 00:22:24,906
To crowd thronging the place,
my brothers and sisters,

227
00:22:25,110 --> 00:22:39,423
party men, district leaders, media
and police, thank you very much.

228
00:22:44,129 --> 00:22:50,261
We very well know how unhappy
you are with the present government.

229
00:22:50,469 --> 00:22:53,438
You paid interest for the
money borrowed by them.

230
00:22:53,638 --> 00:22:56,106
You paid taxes for their wrong doings.

231
00:23:03,148 --> 00:23:14,787
Hail Siva Reddy!

232
00:23:14,993 --> 00:23:19,794
l'm happy to say that Mr.Siva Reddy
will address you shortly.

233
00:23:28,507 --> 00:23:33,968
He is the glimmer of hope
for the minority community.

234
00:23:42,687 --> 00:24:00,368
Hail Siva Reddy!

235
00:24:21,560 --> 00:24:22,857
What will you do for my father?

236
00:24:23,395 --> 00:24:25,693
We'll make him our CM.

237
00:24:25,897 --> 00:24:27,694
Louder please.
Assembly must hear that!

238
00:24:27,899 --> 00:24:29,196
We'll make him our CM.

239
00:24:30,902 --> 00:24:32,870
Now father will address you.

240
00:24:39,244 --> 00:24:43,704
Today l see 2 Hussain Sagars here.

241
00:24:43,915 --> 00:24:45,883
One is flowing under
the tank bunk,

242
00:24:46,151 --> 00:24:48,051
l see the other one flowing here.

243
00:24:50,922 --> 00:24:53,550
When you whistle,
heroes are born.

244
00:24:53,758 --> 00:24:55,885
When you cast vote,
leaders are born.

245
00:24:57,929 --> 00:24:59,226
lf you support one
he becomes a Minister.

246
00:24:59,965 --> 00:25:01,057
Otherwise a wastrel.

247
00:25:03,435 --> 00:25:05,903
When you bless,
leaders live.

248
00:25:06,605 --> 00:25:08,402
When they become despots,
you crush them.

249
00:25:08,773 --> 00:25:11,742
You are the people but
in real mass upheaval.

250
00:25:16,615 --> 00:25:26,923
When you are with me,
no one can dare touch me.

251
00:25:27,325 --> 00:25:34,254
As long as you are with me,
no one can dare touch me.

252
00:25:46,811 --> 00:25:48,108
What happened?- Move.

253
00:25:52,817 --> 00:25:53,784
Call the doctor.

254
00:25:56,154 --> 00:25:57,451
Who killed my father?

255
00:26:22,847 --> 00:26:24,474
Calling control room.

256
00:26:24,583 --> 00:26:25,845
We need more force.

257
00:26:25,951 --> 00:26:26,576
Send it immediately.

258
00:26:26,785 --> 00:26:28,252
