The fun and frolic is
touching the sky...

524
00:49:41,178 --> 00:49:47,913
lt's music of love and
affection all over here...

525
00:50:05,869 --> 00:50:09,498
CBl Office...Hyderabad.
....Old man's room...

526
00:50:09,706 --> 00:50:12,004
Why watch movies early
morning instead of studying?

527
00:50:12,209 --> 00:50:14,507
Okay, l'll find out.

528
00:50:16,046 --> 00:50:17,013
How many films...?

529
00:50:17,214 --> 00:50:18,841
l'm trying to find out the answer.

530
00:50:19,383 --> 00:50:21,010
How many films did Krishna act?

531
00:50:23,220 --> 00:50:27,020
Krishnarjuna Yudham,
Krishna thulabaram,...

532
00:50:27,391 --> 00:50:30,792
The question is not how many films
NTR played Lord Krishna's role.

533
00:50:31,628 --> 00:50:34,461
How many films did
Super star Krishna act?

534
00:50:36,066 --> 00:50:37,294
Around 300 films.

535
00:50:37,501 --> 00:50:39,366
l want the exact figure.

536
00:50:41,405 --> 00:50:42,030
Why?

537
00:50:42,305 --> 00:50:43,863
What bothers you?

538
00:50:44,241 --> 00:50:46,038
My grand daughter is
answering a TV quiz.

539
00:50:48,311 --> 00:50:50,871
l'll find it from some
intelligent person.

540
00:50:51,915 --> 00:50:54,543
Can't you know such simple things?

541
00:50:54,918 --> 00:50:55,714
Why have you come here?

542
00:50:56,586 --> 00:50:57,883
He said you called for me.

543
00:50:58,422 --> 00:51:01,391
Siva Reddy murder case has
been entrusted to us.

544
00:51:03,427 --> 00:51:04,894
Must be dealt very carefully.

545
00:51:06,763 --> 00:51:09,732
Would 2 or 3 days be enough
for you to investigate?

546
00:51:14,271 --> 00:51:15,966
l need 4 or 5 days to read this.

547
00:51:17,007 --> 00:51:18,975
lf you need 4 or 5 days to read this,

548
00:51:19,443 --> 00:51:21,843
how many days will you need
to understand what you read,

549
00:51:22,045 --> 00:51:24,912
how many days will you need to
investigate what you understood,

550
00:51:25,115 --> 00:51:28,642
and how many years will you need
to prepare the investigation report?

551
00:51:29,286 --> 00:51:30,753
l'm not trying to confuse you.

552
00:51:35,692 --> 00:51:36,659
l'll do it.

553
00:51:44,801 --> 00:51:45,529
What is it dear?

554
00:51:46,303 --> 00:51:48,362
Kamal Hasan's first wife's name?

555
00:51:48,638 --> 00:51:50,765
l'm sending 2 men.
They'll tell you.

556
00:51:51,475 --> 00:51:53,443
Your general knowledge is zero. Go.

557
00:51:57,914 --> 00:51:59,438
Hello, it's me.

558
00:51:59,816 --> 00:52:02,114
Find out which TV channel
my grand daughter is watching,

559
00:52:02,486 --> 00:52:04,283
file a case against the
channel & close it down.

560
00:52:04,488 --> 00:52:06,115
Silly questions? ldiot.

561
00:52:08,992 --> 00:52:11,426
Hi Pardhu! How are you?
- lt has been very long since we met.

562
00:52:11,628 --> 00:52:13,858
When did you arrive?
- l saw you when you were a kid.

563
00:52:14,064 --> 00:52:15,793
You've grown very tall.
- l knew you will come.

564
00:52:15,999 --> 00:52:18,160
l've informed all and he too
and brought him here.

565
00:52:21,404 --> 00:52:29,641
l still know your tastes.
Fish curry. Mutton curry.

566
00:52:35,185 --> 00:52:37,153
You finish it off.
Till then l'll wait outside.

567
00:52:37,354 --> 00:52:37,820
No thanks.

568
00:52:38,021 --> 00:52:39,648
You talk. l'll stand outside.

569
00:52:39,856 --> 00:52:41,483
You told me about his arrival.

570
00:52:41,691 --> 00:52:42,817
So, you talk.- No thanks.

571
00:52:43,026 --> 00:52:44,994
lt was Giri who told me
about your arrival.

572
00:52:45,362 --> 00:52:48,160
l'm not in a hurry.
Talk to him first. l'll go out.

573
00:52:48,431 --> 00:52:50,922
Giri stop.
- He is a big nonsense.

574
00:52:51,134 --> 00:52:52,829
You can't stop him
once he starts.

575
00:52:53,870 --> 00:52:54,666
Atleast you tell him.

576
00:52:56,206 --> 00:53:01,838
Wow! He remembers our names.
-You are right.

577
00:53:02,045 --> 00:53:04,843
That's friendship.
You're fit for nothing.

578
00:53:05,715 --> 00:53:09,515
Pardhu, you haven't changed.
- He grew little taller.

579
00:53:12,389 --> 00:53:14,186
You finish.- No, you talk.

580
00:53:15,058 --> 00:53:20,519
After you left the village,
l stopped eating dinner.

581
00:53:20,730 --> 00:53:23,528
Didn't doctor advice you to skip
dinner to reduce your weight?

582
00:53:25,735 --> 00:53:27,532
Just pour your feelings.
l'll stand outside.

583
00:53:27,737 --> 00:53:29,705
Okay. l won't talk. Happy?

584
00:53:30,807 --> 00:53:33,776
So, what's hot, Pardhu?
-You tell me.

585
00:53:34,578 --> 00:53:36,705
Our villagers have got
settled in different places.

586
00:53:37,247 --> 00:53:40,045
Good in studies have become teachers
and others started new schools.

587
00:53:40,250 --> 00:53:41,717
lntelligent are doing
finance business.

588
00:53:41,918 --> 00:53:43,647
Foolish are paying interest
to do agriculture.

589
00:53:44,421 --> 00:53:46,446
Let's go out to have
a smoke and tea.

590
00:53:46,923 --> 00:53:48,220
Just a minute. l'll inform my aunt.

591
00:53:48,425 --> 00:53:51,053
Cigarettes for her? Not necessary.

592
00:53:51,428 --> 00:53:52,725
l'll atleast inform her
about having coffee.

593
00:53:52,963 --> 00:53:53,895
Okay then.

594
00:54:06,776 --> 00:54:08,073
Sambar is tasteless.

595
00:54:09,613 --> 00:54:10,580
Hey boy, change the glass.

596
00:54:10,780 --> 00:54:12,247
He has mistaken water
for sambar.

597
00:54:13,850 --> 00:54:15,078
lt's been very long since we came here.

598
00:54:15,285 --> 00:54:16,081
Do you owe money
to this shopkeeper?

599
00:54:25,295 --> 00:54:29,755
Have you ever felt sad about Shekar?

600
00:54:30,800 --> 00:54:34,258
But l felt many times that
we committed a grave mistake.

601
00:54:34,537 --> 00:54:35,435
Why dig the past?

602
00:54:35,639 --> 00:54:37,266
What he did was wrong?

603
00:54:37,474 --> 00:54:38,270
You could've advised him then.

604
00:54:38,475 --> 00:54:40,943
l was only 10 then.
- He was also 10.

605
00:54:41,478 --> 00:54:44,447
Whatever it is, what you did was wrong.

606
00:54:44,648 --> 00:54:45,444
What did he do?

607
00:54:48,652 --> 00:54:52,110
Waging life...at the age of 10.
ls it right?

608
00:54:52,322 --> 00:54:55,291
Whose life? Who waged?
Who was 10 years old?

609
00:54:55,492 --> 00:54:56,959
l'm not giving you any information.

610
00:54:57,160 --> 00:54:57,956
l'm talking about my feeling.

611
00:54:58,161 --> 00:54:59,128
Why do you feel?

612
00:54:59,329 --> 00:55:01,297
Because it is an incident to feel.

613
00:55:01,498 --> 00:55:02,123
What was the incident?

614
00:55:02,999 --> 00:55:04,967
Why are you scratching old wounds?

615
00:55:05,835 --> 00:55:07,632
Who scratched? What wound?

616
00:55:07,837 --> 00:55:09,964
lt happened 12 years ago.

617
00:55:10,173 --> 00:55:11,800
What happened?

618
00:55:12,008 --> 00:55:13,976
lt's an unforgivable sin.

619
00:55:14,177 --> 00:55:14,643
Hey...

620
00:55:15,712 --> 00:55:17,304
Then, why did you talk about it then?

621
00:55:17,514 --> 00:55:19,812
When l was busy eating
the burnt stuff,

622
00:55:20,016 --> 00:55:24,851
who tortured me like a belly dancer
showing little and covering little?

623
00:55:26,856 --> 00:55:27,823
Tell me what happened?

624
00:55:28,191 --> 00:55:29,158
Tell me what is happening?

625
00:55:29,359 --> 00:55:30,485
Tell me what will happen?

626
00:55:31,194 --> 00:55:32,320
l want to know that now.

627
00:55:33,196 --> 00:55:35,323
l must know.
l must know about it.

628
00:55:35,699 --> 00:55:36,495
Tell him.

629
00:55:38,868 --> 00:55:39,334
No.

630
00:55:39,869 --> 00:55:41,166
He'll say his version
like a lawyer.

631
00:55:41,371 --> 00:55:42,838
l'll say like a judge
acceptable to all.

632
00:55:43,039 --> 00:55:44,666
Whatever it is,
tell it on my face.

633
00:55:46,042 --> 00:55:47,009
12 years back,

634
00:55:47,377 --> 00:55:48,503
in this village,

635
00:55:48,712 --> 00:55:52,512
myself, Pardhu, Giri & priest's son
Shekar were studying 5th std.

636
00:55:52,882 --> 00:55:56,340
One day Pardhu teased
Shekar as coward.

637
00:55:56,619 --> 00:55:57,847
Shekar objected to it.

638
00:55:58,054 --> 00:56:00,022
So, Pardhu challenged
him to a bet.

639
00:56:00,223 --> 00:56:02,691
Visit cemetery at 12 midnight,

640
00:56:02,892 --> 00:56:03,358
l will agree that you're
not a coward.

641
00:56:03,560 --> 00:56:04,686
l will go. l'm not scared.

642
00:56:04,894 --> 00:56:08,352
Okay. We'll keep 4 lemons
on Peer Sahib's grave in the afternoon.

643
00:56:08,565 --> 00:56:09,532
You must bring them
back at night.

644
00:56:09,733 --> 00:56:10,529
Okay sure.

645
00:56:10,734 --> 00:56:12,201
We insisted not to go.

646
00:56:12,402 --> 00:56:15,371
But Pardhu went to Shekar's
house & woke him up.

647
00:56:15,772 --> 00:56:19,367
Shekar alone went to
the cemetery in the night.

648
00:56:19,576 --> 00:56:24,036
He took 3 out of 4 lemons
which we had kept there.

649
00:56:24,781 --> 00:56:26,373
While taking the 4th one,

650
00:56:26,916 --> 00:56:29,043
he felt like someone
pulling him from behind.

651
00:56:29,252 --> 00:56:32,551
He thought it was a ghost.
And his heart stopped beating.

652
00:56:32,922 --> 00:56:34,549
Next morning we saw
it was branch of a tree.

653
00:56:35,992 --> 00:56:37,550
Fear is worse than ghost.

654
00:56:37,927 --> 00:56:38,552
Where is Pardhu?

655
00:56:41,931 --> 00:56:43,899
Sharma hasn't come
out of the shock yet.

656
00:56:44,100 --> 00:56:46,227
You know Shailaja, right?
Shekar's sister.

657
00:56:46,436 --> 00:56:48,404
She was taken to hospital
recently finding difficult to breath.

658
00:56:48,605 --> 00:56:49,731
Doctors said she has
a hole in the heart.

659
00:56:49,939 --> 00:56:52,066
Operation would cost 2 lakhs.

660
00:56:52,275 --> 00:56:54,573
Sharma trusts his god
for everything.

661
00:56:55,111 --> 00:56:59,241
How will god help him
when he's dependent on priest?

662
00:56:59,783 --> 00:57:01,580
Would you like to eat? No.

663
00:57:01,785 --> 00:57:05,585
People come to this
temple to offer prayers,

664
00:57:05,789 --> 00:57:07,586
but never offer anything to god.
Worst fellows.

665
00:57:12,295 --> 00:57:13,421
Shall we go to his house once?

666
00:57:19,469 --> 00:57:20,265
Excuse me sir...

667
00:57:21,304 --> 00:57:22,601
Who is that?

668
00:57:24,974 --> 00:57:26,271
We were on the way to Rajamundry

669
00:57:26,476 --> 00:57:27,943
We had a flat tyre.

670
00:57:28,144 --> 00:57:30,112
Oh no! There is no shop around.

671
00:57:30,647 --> 00:57:32,274
lt's alright.
We will go pushing the car.

672
00:57:34,184 --> 00:57:37,449
Could you please give some water?
- Just a minute.

673
00:57:37,654 --> 00:57:39,952
Also bring something to eat.

674
00:57:45,328 --> 00:57:47,626
We came here to help & not to eat.

675
00:57:47,831 --> 00:57:49,958
Then, tell them that you're Pardhu.

676
00:57:50,166 --> 00:57:51,463
Why lie to them?

677
00:57:51,668 --> 00:57:53,465
l want to help them rather
than telling them the truth.

678
00:57:54,170 --> 00:57:56,968
Help? lt is no child's play?

679
00:57:57,173 --> 00:57:58,640
lt is a heart surgery.- l know.

680
00:57:59,509 --> 00:58:01,807
Do trees in your house bear
money instead of fruits?

681
00:58:02,011 --> 00:58:03,478
ls it not enough if trees in
this house bears money?

682
00:58:08,852 --> 00:58:09,978
What is that?- Money.

683
00:58:10,687 --> 00:58:12,154
Money? How much?

684
00:58:12,355 --> 00:58:14,323
3 lakhs. - 3 lakhs...!?

685
00:58:15,191 --> 00:58:15,987
lsn't that enough?

686
00:58:16,192 --> 00:58:17,159
Have you got it like that?

687
00:58:19,195 --> 00:58:20,662
You threw 3 lakhs
for a hibiscus plant.

688
00:58:20,864 --> 00:58:21,990
Had it been a banana tree,
would you've thrown 5 lakhs?

689
00:58:23,867 --> 00:58:25,334
There is nothing inside.

690
00:58:25,768 --> 00:58:28,168
Just some sweetmeat
offered to the god.

691
00:58:28,371 --> 00:58:31,829
Do you've to feel so bad to say that?
l like it very much.

692
00:58:33,109 --> 00:58:35,168
lt would be handy on
our way back.

693
00:58:35,378 --> 00:58:36,345
lt's alright take it.

694
00:58:37,714 --> 00:58:38,681
Okay.

695
00:58:39,215 --> 00:58:40,842
Let's go.- Just a minute.

696
00:58:41,885 --> 00:58:46,845
lf you don't mistake me,
let me tell you something.

697
00:58:47,056 --> 00:58:48,023
Please.

698
00:58:48,224 --> 00:58:50,749
Ask Aunty to offer prayers
everyday to the Holy Basil plant.

699
00:58:50,960 --> 00:58:51,892
She offers prayers everyday.

700
00:58:52,095 --> 00:58:54,825
Not just prayers, tell her to
offer Hibiscus flowers too.

701
00:58:55,031 --> 00:58:56,692
lt'll give boons...- Come.

702
00:58:57,066 --> 00:58:59,660
Okay.- Tell her to
clean the place too.

703
00:58:59,869 --> 00:59:03,703
There's lot of....dust...

704
00:59:04,240 --> 00:59:06,834
Don't forget to clean it.

705
00:59:16,019 --> 00:59:16,917
Where is he?

706
00:59:26,029 --> 00:59:30,591
Do you know Lord Rama & Hanuman
visited priest's home last night?

707
00:59:30,967 --> 00:59:34,801
Surprised? lt's you the Rama sans
Seetha and l the Hanuman sans tail.

708
00:59:35,138 --> 00:59:38,596
l know that we can gamble & drink
for 6 months if we've Rs.3 lakhs.

709
00:59:38,775 --> 00:59:41,471
Now l know we can take Lord Rama
to priest Sharma's home.

710
00:59:42,045 --> 00:59:43,034
Why are you silent?

711
00:59:43,513 --> 00:59:44,673
God shouldn't be dull.

712
00:59:46,449 --> 00:59:47,381
l'm not a god.

713
00:59:49,519 --> 00:59:51,282
l'm not even an ordinary
human like you.

714
00:59:52,388 --> 00:59:54,117
Thank god didn't say
you weren't Pardhu.

715
00:59:55,291 --> 00:59:58,021
Yes...l'm not Pardhu.

716
01:00:00,463 --> 01:00:01,191
What?

717
01:00:27,657 --> 01:00:30,285
lf you weren't Pardhu,
why did you give money to Sharma?

718
01:00:30,526 --> 01:00:33,256
Because Pardhu was
responsible for their misery.

719
01:00:35,598 --> 01:00:38,431
lf you weren't Murthy's grandson,
why did you come to this village?

720
01:00:40,069 --> 01:00:42,594
l was responsible
for Pardhu's death.

721
01:00:43,473 --> 01:00:47,409
Little confusing but
l've understood it.

722
01:00:50,980 --> 01:00:55,007
One last question.

723
01:00:55,251 --> 01:00:58,015
lf you didn't kill Siva Reddy,
why don't you find who killed him?

724
01:00:58,221 --> 01:00:59,153
Who should l ask?

725
01:00:59,355 --> 01:01:02,518
Siva Reddy is dead,
so you've to ask Baji Reddy.

726
01:01:03,059 --> 01:01:05,357
He's no kid to tell me
on asking him.

727
01:01:05,561 --> 01:01:08,052
You can't leave it,
put police pressure on him.

728
01:01:09,532 --> 01:01:11,659
Police are combing for me.

729
01:01:11,868 --> 01:01:15,702
Oh! Then it's good for you
to be underground.

730
01:01:15,905 --> 01:01:17,236
That's what l'm doing now.

731
01:01:17,440 --> 01:01:18,031
Yes indeed!

732
01:01:18,708 --> 01:01:21,802
You revealed your secrets to me.

733
01:01:22,011 --> 01:01:23,501
What if l tell it to everyone here?

734
01:01:23,846 --> 01:01:25,473
l didn't tell you on asking me,

735
01:01:25,815 --> 01:01:27,009
l told you because l trust you.

736
01:01:27,216 --> 01:01:28,080
Not that...

737
01:01:28,551 --> 01:01:29,711
l trust you because...

738
01:01:30,219 --> 01:01:32,847
...there's no one more trustworthy
like Hanuman to Rama.

739
01:01:38,227 --> 01:01:42,357
Siva Reddy's place of assassination...
Killer's place of operation.

740
01:01:43,599 --> 01:01:46,193
A man slated to become
next CM and one lakh crowd...

741
01:01:46,402 --> 01:01:48,495
20 TV news channels...
Z category security...

742
01:01:48,705 --> 01:01:50,866
20 inches gun and
two kilogram head.

743
01:01:51,074 --> 01:01:52,632
Pull the trigger and gone.

